# Default-pattern allocator golden file.
# Format: <comma-separated-files>|<args>|<expected-stdout>
# Newlines in expected stdout encoded as literal \n.
# Empty setup means empty corpus.
# This file pins the regression boundary for the default-pattern allocator
# behaviour: byte-for-byte identical stdout under {number:04d}.

||0001
0001-foo.md|--count 1|0002
0002-something.md|--count 1|0003
0001-first.md,0005-fifth.md||0006
0001-first.md|--count 3|0002\n0003\n0004
0042-foo.md|--count 1|0043
0001-foo.md,0002-bar.md|--count 1|0003
0099-baz.md|--count 1|0100
